# --- Secrets / local env ---
.env
.env.*
*.local
secrets/
*.key
*.pem

# NOTE: ~/brain and ~/sources (the synthesis and immutable raw layers) live
# OUTSIDE this repo, in the user's home directory. They are personal data and
# are never part of this repository — nothing to ignore here, just a reminder.

# The populated config (~/brain/config/sources.yml) is personal data and lives
# outside the repo. We DO ship the template below, so do NOT ignore it:
!config/sources.example.yml
